          <h1>My Introduction</h1>

          <p>
           Hello, and welcome to my personal portfolio. My name is Scott Sousa. Here you will find information about my life, a detailed description of my
           car (and why it's so special to me), my photography, my design work, and maybe a little more.  I currently reside in New Bedford, MA.
           I am 20 years old and loving life. My cat <a href="subpages/myphoto/animals/animals.html" title="Mustache">Mustache</a> rocks! I am a student at
           <a href="http://www.jwu.edu" title="Johnson &amp; Wales University">Johnson &amp; Wales University</a> and I'm on pace to graduate in May of 2010.
           I have my Associate's Degree in Web Site Development. I am majoring in Graphics and New Media for my Bachelor's Degree.
           I absolutely love <a href="http://www.nhra.com" title="NHRA">drag racing</a>. I am also a freelance photographer. If you would like to know more,
           please have a look at my <a href="subpages/mylife/mylife.html" title="My Life">life</a>.
          </p>


